name: MenuoftheDay
0:
”Alexa, ask menu of the day what is the menu at South?”
”Alexa, ask menu of the day what's the menu at West?”
”Alexa, ask menu of the day what is the menu at North today?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: menu of the day
des:
Find out the menu for any of Rice's six serveries!

The menus are constantly updated to the upcoming menu for the day at each of the serveries: North, South, West, Baker, Sid, and Seibel.
 
So what are you waiting for? Ask Menu of the Day about what's being served at any of the serveries so that you can always make the best decision about which servery to go to!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
